      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains taut with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the signature communicative steering and balanced turn-in these chassis are known for. A mechanically robust driver\u2019s car that delivers a visceral, analog performance experience.",
